Definition: You will be shown two proteins. Your job is to determine if the two protein interact based on {Relationship Summary}. {Task-Specific Relationship}You may only output yes or no. If the protein shown is the one described, you should respond yes. Otherwise, you should respond no.
Relationship Summary: the degree of homology of the interactors
Task-Specific Relationship: Two proteins would have more potential to interact, if their homologous proteins exist in proximity of each other in a known PPI network.
